Exoplanet Characterization:

Atmospheric Studies: Investigate the atmospheres of exoplanets to identify potential biosignatures.
Habitable Zones: Explore the concept of habitable zones around stars and identify exoplanets within these regions.

Galactic and Cosmological Studies:

Galactic Dynamics: Analyze the structure and dynamics of galaxies to understand their formation and evolution.
Cosmic Microwave Background (CMB): Investigate the CMB for insights into the early universe and cosmological paramerers.
